(8, 12, '<h2 style=\"text-align: center;\">Agreement between User and Ilum&trade;&nbsp;</h2>\r\n\r\n<p>Welcome to Ilum&trade;. The Ilum&trade;&nbsp;website (the \"Site\") is comprised of various web pages operated by Ilum, Inc. (\"Ilum\"). Ilum&trade; is offered to you conditioned on your acceptance without modification of the terms, conditions, and notices contained herein (the \"Terms\"). Your use of Ilum&trade; constitutes your agreement to all such Terms. Please read these terms carefully, and keep a copy of them for your reference.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Ilum&trade; is a digital gifting, cloud based platform that allows users to send one another items from a menu, from a remote location and in real time. It&rsquo;s app and software platform use API integrations to process transactions from the app to the locations point of sale system, creating a fun, spontaneous and secure way to send someone a gift. The app also features a private social feed, documenting and storytelling gifting transactions as well as a digital wallet to process secure transactions.</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Privacy&nbsp;</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Your use of Ilum&trade; is subject to Ilum&trade;&#39;s <a href=\"/legal/privacy-policy\">Privacy Policy</a>. Please review our Privacy Policy, which also governs the Site and informs users of our data collection practices.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Electronic Communications&nbsp;</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>Visiting Ilum&trade; or sending emails to Ilum constitutes electronic communications. You consent to receive electronic communications and you agree that all agreements, notices, disclosures and other communications that we provide to you electronically, via email and on the Site, satisfy any legal requirement that such communications be in writing.&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<h5>Your Account&nbsp;</h5>\r\n\r\n<p>If you use this site, you are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your account and password and for restricting access to your computer, and you agree to accept responsib